---
source: src/pack/mod.rs
assertion: context packing uses tiktoken-rs cl100k_base token counting by default
schema:
  strategy: tiktoken_cl100k_base
contracts:
  - default token estimation routes through tiktoken-rs cl100k_base
  - empty and whitespace-only inputs count as zero tokens
  - known short strings match cl100k_base token counts
  - CJK text is not under-counted by the legacy character heuristic
  - repeated estimates are deterministic for identical input
evidence:
  - TokenEstimationStrategy::TiktokenCl100kBase
  - estimate_tokens_default
  - estimate_tokens_tiktoken_matches_known_short_strings
  - estimate_tokens_tiktoken_is_more_accurate_than_heuristic_for_cjk
  - estimate_tokens_tiktoken_is_deterministic
